# qa_quicklook setting-set "working overlay" — per-operator scratch
# space.  Master files at conf/<name>.toml symlink into here while
# the dashboard has unsaved local edits; the directory itself stays
# untracked so a dirty working tree doesn't follow operators around.
conf/working/

# Cross-shifter sync — Google service-account JSON keys.  The default
# storage path is ~/.config/qa_quicklook/sheets-sa.json (outside the
# worktree); these patterns are belt-and-braces against the day someone
# accidentally drops a key under the repo root.
*sa.json
*service-account*.json
*-sheets-*.json
# Reverse-merge snapshot baseline — operator-local state that should
# never be committed.  Lives under ~/.cache/qa_quicklook/ in the real
# install; the pattern catches strays from running the CLI inside the
# repo with --snapshot-path overrides.
sheets_last_pushed.json